- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper's focus on natural language understanding and use of machine learning techniques make it a likely candidate for this category.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society): The paper's focus on the medical domain may also make it relevant to the intersection of computers and society.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper's use of natural language understanding techniques may also make it relevant to information retrieval tasks.
